		<p><span class="style_bold">What to bring to camp</span></p>
		<ul>
		<li>Backpack
		</li>
		<li>Hat
		</li>
		<li>Suntan lotion
		</li>
		<li>Jeans
		</li>
		<li>Cotton shirt to wear...this keeps you cool and covered
		</li>
		<li>Jacket...just in case
		</li>
		<li>Diary or disposable camera (with you name on it)
		</li>
		<li>And lastly Healthy lunch snacks and drinks in reusable containers
		</li>
		</ul>
		<p><span class="style_bold">Easter Camps</span><br />
		Bring lots of extra layers and gloves. Always bring more clothes then you need when you ride, 
		you can always strip layers.</p>
